{"word":"G279 - ἀμετανόητος - ametanóētos - am-et-an-o'-ay-tos - Impenitent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμετανόητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ametanóētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-et-an-o'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Impenitent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குணப்படாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"Admitting no change of mind (amendment), unrepentant, impenitent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3340 - μετανοέω - metanoéō - met-an-o-eh'-o/3340\">G3340</a>; <i>unrepentant:</i> - impenitent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1270/1270\">G1270</a>, <a href=\"#/G1271/1271\">G1271</a>, <a href=\"#/G1425/1425\">G1425</a>, <a href=\"#/G1771/1771\">G1771</a>, <a href=\"#/G2132/2132\">G2132</a>, <a href=\"#/G2133/2133\">G2133</a>, <a href=\"#/G2657/2657\">G2657</a>, <a href=\"#/G279/279\">G279</a>, <a href=\"#/G3340/3340\">G3340</a>, <a href=\"#/G3539/3539\">G3539</a>, <a href=\"#/G3540/3540\">G3540</a>, <a href=\"#/G3559/3559\">G3559</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563/3563\">G3563</a>, <a href=\"#/G4306/4306\">G4306</a>, <a href=\"#/G4307/4307\">G4307</a>, <a href=\"#/G453/453\">G453</a>, <a href=\"#/G454/454\">G454</a>, <a href=\"#/G5282/5282\">G5282</a>, <a href=\"#/G5283/5283\">G5283</a>"}]}